t: "Divorced women must wait three monthly cycles Ë¹before they can re-marryËº. It is not lawful for them to conceal what Allah has created in their wombs,Â if they Ë¹trulyËº believe in Allah and the Last Day. And their husbands reserve the right to take them back within that period if they desire reconciliation. Women have rights similar to those of men equitably, although men have a degree Ë¹of responsibilityËº above them. And Allah is Almighty, All-Wise"